=== USAGE ===

$ chef-solo-flight <command> <server_1> [server_2] [...]

Where command is one of:
 - bootstrap
 - update
 - help
 - version

Server should be in the form of a standard username/server spec:
 - server.com
 - cname.server.com
 - user@server.com
 - user@cname.server.com
 - user@server.com:22
 - user@cname.server.com:22
